# OpenCode Skills Configuration for Dotfiles

This file declares which skills should be auto-loaded when working on this dotfiles repository.

## Core Skills

Always load these skills when working in this project:

| Skill | When |
|---|---|
| **git** | Always — dotfiles is version-controlled |
| **mcp** | Always — GitHub ops use github-mcp tools by default |
| **docker** | When compose.yml or Dockerfile present |
| **python** | When .py files or pyproject.toml present |
| **nodejs** | When .ts/.js files in .opencode/plugins |
| **yaml** | When .yaml or .yml files present |

## Project-Specific

- **Dotfiles maintainer:** Delegate cross-platform changes to `dotfiles-maintainer` subagent
- **POSIX only:** All scripts are `#!/bin/sh` — no bash-specific syntax
- **Hardcoded path:** Uses `$HOME/.dotfiles`

